 "overview": "\u003Cp\u003EBrighter Option, an independent software development company have created SAM, an innovative Facebook advertising management tool providing businesses of all sizes and budgets with the controls and analytics to launch, monitor and optimize highly targeted Facebook advertising campaigns.\u003C/p\u003E\n\n\u003Cp\u003EKey features and benefits include:\n\u00e2\u20ac\u00a2 Efficient campaign creation\n\u00e2\u20ac\u00a2 Extensive Reporting\n\u00e2\u20ac\u00a2 Advanced analytics\n\u00e2\u20ac\u00a2 Intelligent optimization\n\u00e2\u20ac\u00a2 Advanced conversion data\n\u00e2\u20ac\u00a2 Optimization towards key performance indicators\n\u00e2\u20ac\u00a2 Campaign scheduling\n\u00e2\u20ac\u00a2 Outstanding customer support\u003C/p\u003E\n\n\u003Cp\u003EBrighter Option offer comprehensive training, insight and support to ensure that SAM is being used to its full capacity. Advice and information about campaign set ups and performance insights are also freely given.\u003C/p\u003E",
